name: 50 - 200 flaps per second
description: I had never seen a Hummingbird before visiting California and I initially thought this was a Hummingbird Moth which are fairly common in Europe and look very much like a Hummingbird. I got hyped when I realised that it was in fact a real Hummingbird and managed to capture it in this shot. While it's not perfect I'm happy with it.
